    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  To be diagnosed with hepatocellular carcinoma in last 3 months

          -  To be older than 18 years old

          -  To sign informed consent form (ICF)

